KCC Introduction: Kucoin community chain (KCC) is a high-performanceAnd decentralized public chain based on Ethereum source code, Which is led by the majority of community developers and Community users.Its purpose is to solve the problems such as low performance and high cost of public chain, So as to provide Community users with more high-speed, convenient and low-cost experience Of blockchain.
kcc1: Fully compatible with Ethereum and ERC-20 smart contracts, With extremely low migration costs
kcc2: KuCoin Token (KCS) will serve as the only core fuel and native token for KCC and can be used in scenarios such as gas fee payment
kcc3: A block every 3 seconds results in faster transaction confirmation and higher chain performance
kcc4: Proof of Staked Authority (PoSA) consensus algorithm, high efficiency, security and stability
